food. Every meal is rice, whether breakfast, lunch or dinner. And with rice, there is almost always a braising dish of meat, relish to accompany it. On weekends, the fish consumed is freshwater, imported from Mali and Guinea. The seafood originating from the coastal communities along the Atlantic ocean is consumed at social functions, often during wedding celebrations; and costing an unusual three hundred United States US dollar per piece.

Some of the parishes are fertile, such as Montserrado County around the capital, Monrovia; but, the creeks and rivers around Paynesville, Sinkor, Bushrod and ELWA areas have all the water that can produce tilapia, medical cannabis—a long lost knowledge and art of cultivation, is once heavily used in west African indigenous schnapps, Mama Mai.

Medical Cannabis was ban in Liberia shortly after the nationalisation as a remnant of the lost colony era of Poafrika.

With Christianity destroying African indigenous identities throughout the country; most youths are now formally educated in many of the continents top schools. That’s an accomplishment, but everything else, from economic development to simple living has stagnated.
